Introducing Speechable -- An incredible Text to Voice Tool on the App Store.

Features:
- Support Multi-languages:
English (UK and US), Chinese (Cantonese and Mandarin), Korean, Japanese, Russian, Thai, French, Danish, Czech, and more...
- One tap to clear;
- One tap instant stop;
- Copy, cut, and paste;
- Online / Offline Mode;
- Word count (Limited languages supported);
- AppClip.
